la Defensa|accessdate=8 July 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308193855/http://www.umbv.edu.ve/amcsb/index.php/mision|archive-date=8 March 2016|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n\n<blockquote>''Be a top-level military academy composed of the professional and military field, health oriented training for medics, military surgeons and nurses, military excellence through scientific, humanist principals of [[medical education]], military doctrine and efficient performance for all levels of FANB medical care; with emphasis on active participation in the development of a [[Self care#Culture of Health|culture of health]] and comprehensive prevention.''</blockquote>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n[[Category:Bolivarian Military University of Venezuela]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox university\n| name           =  Military Academy of Health Sciences\n| native_name    =  Academia Militar de Medicina\n| image          =  Military_Academy_of_Health_Sciences_logo.png\n| image_size     =  150px\n| caption        = \n| latin_name     = \n| motto          = \n| motto_lang     = \n| mottoeng       = \n| established    = 2013\n| closed         = \n| type           = [[Military Academy|Military]]\n| parent         = [[Military academy of Venezuela|Bolivarian Military University of Venezuela]]\n| affiliation    = \n| endowment      = \n| budget         = \n| officer_in_charge = \n| chairman       = \n| chancellor     = \n| president      = \n| vice-president = \n| superintendent = \n| provost        = \n| vice_chancellor= \n| rector         = \n| principal      = \n| dean           = \n| director       = \n| head_label     = \n| head           = \n| academic_staff = \n| administrative_staff = \n| students       = \n| undergrad      = \n| postgrad       = \n| doctoral       = \n| other          = \n| city           = [[Caracas]]\n| state          = \n| province       = \n| country        = [[Venezuela]]\n| coor           = \n| campus         = \n| former_names   = \n| free_label 